{
  "guid": "pycv",
  "name": "Poly CV",
  "description": "A polyphonic MIDI/CV converter that takes the polysynth control logic from other polysynths and uses it not to produce sound but to output CVs and gates. This makes it most obviously useful as a MIDI/CV converter, but it can also function as a chord/arpeggio engine controlled by CV/gate inputs. Please refer to the section 'Common polysynth features' for additional details.",
